data.name: label1.Text
data.value: In this live demostration you'll be able to see the applications of object detection and computer vision with this self-driving car! not only that, it's fully interactive, you'll be able to control the car manually and set the car to computer controlled mode where the car is drven by algorithms alone!

data.name: label4.Text
data.value: press file to access the options: --> connect the camera by clicking play --> isolate the object you want to track using the sliders and the video feed in the top left --> connect to the car by pressing scan ports --> select the port that isn't port 1 --> then press connect
